title: Parvati - Area bounded by Singhagad Road on the north, Singhagad Road on the west, Southern boundary of P
clause_text: Parvati - Area bounded by Singhagad Road on the north, Singhagad Road on the west, Southern boundary of P.L. Deshpande Udyan on the south, and Road from over bridge upto Laxminagar and western boundary of Tulsibagwale Colony in S.No.89, 90 etc. of Parvati on the east. Chatushrungi - S.No.105, 106 pt., 107 pt. etc. of village Bhamburda.
section: Note - This regulation stand modify if modified by the Government / Collector.
